  <h1>Audra Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Package:</strong> com.bright.player.audra</p>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Audra is an audio player app designed to let you enjoy your music and audio files seamlessly. 
      The app does not collect or store any personal user data directly. 
      However, it may integrate third-party SDKs such as Google AdMob, Firebase Crashlytics, and Firebase Analytics. 
      These services may automatically collect some non-personal information to provide ads, analyze app usage, and improve performance.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Third-Party Services Used</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google AdMob</strong> – Used to display ads. May use Advertising ID and cookies to personalize ads and measure performance.</li>
      <li><strong>Firebase Crashlytics</strong> – Used for crash reporting and stability monitoring.</li>
      <li><strong>Firebase Analytics</strong> – Used to understand app usage and improve user experience.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Required Permissions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE – Access audio files stored on your device.</li>
      <li>READ_MEDIA_AUDIO – Access audio content in your media library.</li>
      <li>INTERNET – Stream online audio and show ads.</li>
      <li>ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE – Check network connectivity for streaming.</li>
      <li>FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MEDIA_PLAYBACK – Enable continuous audio playback in the foreground.</li>
      <li>FOREGROUND_SERVICE – Support background services.</li>
      <li>POST_NOTIFICATIONS – Notify you about playback, updates, or other app events.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:briansmith4r@gmail.com">briansmith4r@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>

